      <title>埃塞俄比亚称因平等而扣留“负担得起”的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/ethiopia-optimistic-on-debt-deal-with-creditors-in-early-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四参加与财政部官员电话会议的投资者表示，埃塞俄比亚政府计划于明年初与债券持有人就 10 亿美元欧元债券的重组条款达成协议，该债券本月拒绝支付息票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-14/ethiopia-optimistic-on-debt-deal-with-creditors-in-early-2024</guid>
